# Changelog

All notable changes to PixelDrop will be documented here.
Format loosely follows [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/).

---

## [Unreleased]
- Dark mode support for the summary report (lol)
- WebP animated image support (maybe)

---

## [1.2.0] - 2024-11-03
### Added
- Watch mode (`pixeldrop watch`) for auto-compression on file save
- Support for `.webp` format

### Fixed
- CLI crash when output directory doesn't exist yet (now auto-creates it)
- Incorrect byte count in summary when processing large batches

---

## [1.1.0] - 2024-09-18
### Added
- `pixeldrop.config.json` support for persistent configuration
- `--preserve-structure` flag to mirror source directory layout in output

### Changed
- Quality defaults tuned: JPEG 80, PNG 90, WebP 85

---

## [1.0.1] - 2024-08-05
### Fixed
- Panic on empty directory input
- Wrong exit code on compression failure

---

## [1.0.0] - 2024-07-20
### Added
- Initial release ðŸŽ‰
- Compress JPEG and PNG via CLI
- Batch directory processing
- Summary report output
